Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！依文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依文…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里呢  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Malleus Aquilonis{\r}\N冰神战锤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由依文同学组织的地狱训练终于告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就代表是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大海啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们涅吉魔社正在享受海边的短暂休假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉小弟是第一次来日本的海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  人可真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就像我们当初约定好的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩个痛快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩个尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易来趟海边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不游泳岂不是白来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来和我比比看谁先游到那边的岩石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的海滩热闹非凡  大家说是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…为什么班长也在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里说起来可是涅吉魔社（暂定）的合宿活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么连你们这些人也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果班长和裕奈  以及莳绘她们也都跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝们可真是活力无限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  你们不能跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道会遇到什么危险的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真是死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们不跟你们去那些危险的地方就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么定下来喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个暑假  我们大家一起去英国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂！  别自作主张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如此这般  最后还是决定了大家一起去英国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为这样骚动总算是平息了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长  小莳等人  她们基本上都是知道涅吉弟弟的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才一起跟去威尔士的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们二位在去威尔士之前  最好也先考虑些深层接触涅吉弟弟的方案比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啥…深层接触…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们很走运地了解了\N关于涅吉弟弟的魔法和他的过去  这就是你们的优势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光知道傻玩的话  搞不好会让谁把涅吉弟弟给抢走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话…话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我们能学会魔法  并且站在能直接帮助涅吉老师的立场上这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是纯属偶然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小莳就很可爱  真是羡慕她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长也是赛过模特般的好身材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为人正直清廉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人要是动真格的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许没什么胜算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香你还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看我根本就是一副惨不忍睹的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  感觉未来好暗淡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师身边还有明日菜同学在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学她又是怎么想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅…涅吉老师和明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人独处难不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱特训之后的放松真是格外舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干…干嘛啊  突然一本正经地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要感谢也应该感谢大伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是班长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙知道你的目的之后  就非常关心这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前一阵子的那些情报也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那两个人之间的关系当中有一些特殊的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然那究竟算不算是恋爱类的感情这一点上还有商讨余地…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然听不太明白  总之就是说他们两个人在打情骂俏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  和香你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那话不是我说的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我辛辛苦苦大老远跑来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他却和那傻呼呼的的女人卿卿我我缠缠绵绵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什么时候涅吉他都傻得要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Fortress Ra Tes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Release Lilios
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅～吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Anya Flame Buster Kick{\r}\N阿妮亚火焰超级踢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞搞搞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,召来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她一下子冲过来想干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们的敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…刚刚那招…莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  表现不错嘛  居然能避开刚刚那一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来魔法的修行你从来都没有偷过懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是一点没变啊  小不点外加傻呼呼的涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦！阿妮亚难道就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阿妮亚会来日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不应该在伦敦当占卜师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用问吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是来带你回…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的披风怎么着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这件好贵的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烫烫烫烫烫  不好了  屁股着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救火救火  快来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿…阿妮亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是来做什么的啊  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是来带你回去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个闲不住的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说  赶快跟我回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去？  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放了暑假你还是不回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才代替寂寞的涅佳涅姐姐来找你回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,带我回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  她是涅吉故乡村落里那个小大人的青梅竹马…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了的话就赶快跟我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我特意去了一趟麻帆良学园  结果你还不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我还特意去调查一番  跑来这个土气的国家的土气的海滩找你的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉他回英国之前还有事要办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在涅吉担任顾问的部团正在这里进行合宿活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能再稍微等一等？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个一来就跟人套近乎的女人  我记得是叫神乐坂明日菜的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…照片上最常出现的…最需要留心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且一见面就被她看到失态的一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.72,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（阿妮亚的主观视点）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这什么身材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说涅吉他就是因为这个才不愿意回去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人呢！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家涅吉让你多费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不必客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说来  一见面就耍出那种魔法招数  还客气个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今后涅吉就由我来照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚赶这么久的路也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少先吃个饭再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刺…刺身  还有天妇罗这里都吃得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刺身…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天妇罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师的青梅竹马？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…好像单纯只是来叫涅吉早点回老家的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同年龄的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来稍微年长一岁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美女？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让开一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些全部吃掉都可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？  好全新的触感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都吃这些的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本美食最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊…不是小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轮不到你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢…涅吉弟弟的青梅竹马  当然是小孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这下可算是没白来一趟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  竟然会为刺身和天妇罗上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚真是贪吃鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为你总是不回去  才害我特地跑来这个土里土气的日本来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来…阿妮亚你修行的情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还顺利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我？  我的修行很顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最初是比较辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在和城里人的关系也搞得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一提起丽晶街后巷的占卜师阿妮亚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是小有名气啦…在一部分人当中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来你又怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被要求当老师这种你无法完成的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我？  我也很顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？  照片我看过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？什么意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小不点又傻呼呼又土气的涅吉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被一群漂亮的大姐姐围着嘻嘻哈哈  哪还有心思修行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是打心里在认真做老师这个工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全是女生还不因为是女子学校  我又有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我可没有整天嘻嘻哈哈  身高也有见长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也每天都有成长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小不点不管再怎么成长估计也没差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要比一比？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是大哥获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你踮脚了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少找借口了  我才没踮脚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也不会输你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小孩子气呢  傻瓜涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总说我是小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看这回阿妮亚才算是小不点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是小朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这两人本来就是小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人欣慰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不准呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这下搞不好危险了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟的态度啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还看不出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那孩子说话时的涅吉非常随意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说基本没什么顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且偶尔还会没大没小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据我所知  只有对高畑老师和小太郎说话时  涅吉才会那么随意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…对卡莫君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他对3-A的所有人毫无例外都是客客气气的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟和3-A的所有同学之间都存在着内心障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,内心障碍？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而和那个孩子之间就不存在这层障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这代表什么大家应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:50.94,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（就是说）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可笑  太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…你别吃得太快了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼！  一天到晚傻呼呼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看…饭都沾到脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不管怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚  很感谢你特地过来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才不是为了你而来的呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是因为涅佳涅姐姐拜托我才来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后跟涅吉老师配成对的可能性最大…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸…幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一…一堆女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她…她们就是那些照片上的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被击倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面的印象很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉的诸位学生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是安娜·可可罗瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事情怎么就复杂起来了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实涅吉老师周围的形势真是越来越复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过阿妮亚她满可爱的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是露天浴场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的同伴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好像知道魔法的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的  我们都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我叫宫崎和香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫绫濑夕映
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…阿妮亚跟涅吉老师一样  在伦敦修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我修行的是占卜师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…阿妮亚你已经有搭档了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,经过那个…契约…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,契…你们连这都知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情还没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,选搭档这种事情必须得慎重才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅…涅吉他又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会和那个叫明日菜什么的已经做过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个傻瓜他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  明日菜她是敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还用问吗？  当然是因为胸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胸大的女人都是敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  男人总会被那种东西给骗得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  所以要赶紧从这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛  那小鬼是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师的青梅竹马不会就是她吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不大  但形状很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是美胸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人也是敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她们一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对大海没兴趣  但我喜欢温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她们？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新的敌人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  不是小阿妮亚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那一下摇得好夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  那个孩子就是传说中的阿妮亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  你们三个已经打成一片啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的温泉感觉如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚  回头我们互相擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤姐的胸部又变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么搞得啊  这个班级
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不是都只有15岁左右的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本就是让之前那个明日菜变得不值一提的巨乳军团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀气！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会输给你这种小丫头的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人虽然不是巨乳  但身材却非常之好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咕  四面楚歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们另当别论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们定能成为好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里…不必
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是一个巨乳巢穴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再待在这种地方的话  涅吉肯定就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是得下定决心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…赶快把涅吉给抓回威尔士去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被发现了会怎么样你应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊  知不知道到底是多亏了谁你才能到这里来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯什么嗯  你根本没在听我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是谁擅自闯进禁咒书库里去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  涅吉快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没事  马上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊  赶快把书扔了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  马上就能全记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个傻瓜  快跑起来啊  难道你想被抓住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  马上就跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜傻瓜傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了你这家伙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在你就什么事也做不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我到日本来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要把涅吉给带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  起来啦  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回乡的准备已经做好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,起来啦  赶快给我换…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说涅吉你又…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼啊  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Anya Flame Knuckle{\r}\N阿妮亚火焰铁拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老毛病又发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你这个家伙一大清早的搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女孩真火暴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟涅吉的姐姐很像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到现在还是不那样做就睡不着觉吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才只是因为睡迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是那个和涅佳涅姐很像的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…确实有那么三分像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但姐姐她可没你这副傻样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比你可漂亮多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你再说一遍？  死小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然钻到这个傻女人的被窝里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好色涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说我那是不由自主…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪我总是讨厌死小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦  我们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下啦  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天不是说了涅吉他现在还不能回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么权利对我指手画脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么权利…当然因为我是涅吉的搭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行啦  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚她还没那啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是知道我们所有人都做过了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搭是什么意思？  大白痴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  卡莫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于卡片的功能方面我有点事情想请…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔  你们想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘  嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚啊  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是很重要的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上啊…实际上呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的所有七个女孩子竟然全都跟涅吉弟弟是搭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟想说什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么啊  春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早会露馅的  有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚啊  为什么那么急着赶回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说阿妮亚你喜欢涅吉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  把涅吉一个人丢在这么多女孩子中间是比较挂心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是这样呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来暂时就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有两下子呢  木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是完美的危机应对能力  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱啊  那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Pacchi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是Pactio吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不和大家一起玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来海边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:22:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要你啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才完全不是那么回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才？  什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她们说我喜欢你啊什么的那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那事？  那还用说嘛  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你这家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没和那些漂亮大姐姐中的谁卿卿我我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情当然不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她们都是我的学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不缠着你要马上回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不用强行带他回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但大清早那情形  怎么想这里的环境对涅吉的修行绝对不利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  还是需要我在这里好好看着他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这么决定了  我们赶快回到大伙身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下…我说  别拉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人数突然增加  无法为你们提供第二晚的客房
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不让各位挤一个大房间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里  本来就是我们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小事一桩  这样反而更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡涅吉弟弟身边的人可要小心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.90,0:24:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟啊  有时候没有姐姐的温暖就睡不着的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.30,0:24:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时睡迷糊之后可能会一下抱住旁边的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.47,0:24:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.85,0:24:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,惊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.60,0:24:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到涅吉老师竟然有这么让人又喜又羞的癖好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.38,0:24:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个好机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.11,0:24:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  我得好好看着  别让他又犯早上的迷糊事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.47,0:24:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能够睡在涅吉老师的旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.73,0:24:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.95,0:24:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枕头大战啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.16,0:25:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没有和大小姐共枕了呢  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.25,0:25:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.81,0:25:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们睡一床被子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.17,0:25:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这…这…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.03,0:25:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说！  你们这帮人给我老实睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.88,0:25:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果呢  还没决出胜负  大家就抱头大睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.60,0:25:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白天晚上都疯成那样子不困才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.10,0:25:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也躺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.19,0:25:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.31,0:25:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能睡着呢  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.59,0:25:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.76,0:25:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是要怎么样才能获取涅吉身边的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.26,0:25:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干净利索点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.76,0:25:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么干净利索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.97,0:25:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈…哈呜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.80,0:25:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么  这个杀气是？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.59,0:25:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮大姐姐真打算去抢涅吉身边的位置？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.93,0:25:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  尽可能自然一点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.47,0:25:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一边装成睡相不好  一边接近涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  那帮人是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.10,0:26:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.60,0:26:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.57,0:26:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去洗手间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.00,0:26:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.98,0:26:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.57,0:26:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.01,0:26:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟糕  一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.61,0:26:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…怎么会…真是天上掉下的馅饼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.01,0:26:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.55,0:26:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请用我温暖的胸来…呜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.79,0:26:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  班长  我从小就睡相不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.15,0:26:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁信啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.65,0:26:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…骗你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟我收下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.08,0:26:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  到我的胸怀里来  涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.24,0:26:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Anya Over Head…{\r}\N阿妮亚倒挂金钩…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.65,0:26:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.39,0:26:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}…Kick！{\r}\N…踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.18,0:27:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你对涅吉老师做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.91,0:27:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  挨那一下子涅吉死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.58,0:27:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.47,0:27:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还不醒…  啊  已经昏过去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.77,0:27:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.64,0:27:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好机会啊  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.08,0:27:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天上掉馅饼了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.70,0:27:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先请
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.52,0:27:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅…涅吉老师  和香不才…  请多…多…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.80,0:27:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.41,0:27:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不允许先偷吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.81,0:27:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.16,0:27:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这帮人…还是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.15,0:27:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有点变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.61,0:27:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱是不分年龄的嘛
